ce.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5601dce19344780975fdc59479d28f32ebbe8f88","tid":634660,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e06b3da0d1f7cb8478f365fab9c9b69b71993f48","tid":634660,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:53:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊間大學?</blockquote><br />\n等咗咁耐終於有人問<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"第一個正常問題"},{"pid":"ab64994909d8d8aadd8b94c522bef79de9fbfa5b","tid":634660,"uid":56550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:33:00.000Z","msg":"OU社服<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417a05c464b533dcfabaa91e733522db0a017a70","tid":634660,"uid":173002,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29c9a98244e3a00514479636daade4387a20489f","tid":634660,"uid":1067,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:44:42.000Z","msg":"仲以為佢訂咗又唔俾錢又唔聽電話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"消費者委員會曾指出，買家如果已經付費，食物就屬於買家，買家確實可以放棄已付費的食物。<br />\n<br />\n以前曾經係快餐店做過短期，見過唔少人係網上付費後沒有黎取食物，有啲左打極電話都唔通，有啲回覆就話俾左錢但係宜家唔要，叫我哋自行處理，但係唔知之後又會唔會要返，食物又唔可以放過夜，最後全部垃圾桶。"},{"pid":"bf42b411e1923c46088fa57032ab93fbe3f92697","tid":634660,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"年年都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31d039f933b43476289b2a839042b963d2a7b96a","tid":634660,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bebf92bfb402f139abd8bcb8b57daae06ef03a11","tid":634660,"uid":146243,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"80b20a67dfa060c3f0c53e2563959c1df3fc991e","tid":634660,"uid":18925,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:50:20.000Z","msg":"店主在Facebook表示，學生雖要求50元一盤，但最終一盤需130元，但「三盒牛腩飯唔到價錢，可我哋肯定130蚊在外面係買唔到」<br />\n<br />\n我有冇理解錯 <br />\n佢地只係出$50 買價值$130既食物<br />\n人地照接黎做點知冇人黎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T13:00:44.000Z","msg":"我理解 <br />\n學生r出價：50<br />\n店主還價：130<br />\n<br />\n市價: &gt;130<br />\n<br />\n咁店主覺得冇癮好正常 見你學生平比你咁 自己一擔心機 哂曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:57:25.000Z","msg":"大學生已經培養出賤種心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市價130 出半價都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾抵俾人串"},{"pid":"d26d61830e08b9bc050929ab308f053ea3b68a86","tid":634660,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:58:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fb5d81657588971da47423c771dc34bae64c6a","tid":634660,"uid":119450,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"06e504b92f58681cfe32a677ad2cca24a3281f86","tid":634660,"uid":85819,"like":15,"dislike":44,"score":-29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T12:36:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:02:54.000Z","msg":"店主做普通街外人生意咪唔理囉<br />\n成日都有人訂完花唔攞<br />\n收錢咪算<br />\n<br />\n係做你大學生生意俾你還價<br />\n乞人優惠<br />\n態度又串串貢<br />\n最後電話又唔撚聽<br />\n<br />\n根本係班大學生作賤攞黎俾人串<br />\n你唔尊重人 店主洗撚尊重返你<br />\n唔講唔係人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac0e8b9140c52af047cbe74398268681044a034","tid":634660,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"個店主又係on9<br />\n唔黎你咪派街坊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea24a643f785440d3ff2e7dd84c74c0c9ebba06","tid":634660,"uid":69885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ac0e8b9140c52af047cbe74398268681044a034","tid":634660,"uid":108090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T1